Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93239,94949}Meimi Haneoka is 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:38.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95241,98661}By day, she is a happy student of\NSt. Paulia School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99370,102498}But at night, she becomes the thief,\NSt. Tail, to do good deeds…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:46.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102540,106294}for all who ask for help from Seira,\Na nun in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:51.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107420,111382}Looking to capture the elusive St. Tail\Nis an amateur detective…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111674,114010}and Meimi's classmate, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:59.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114469,119265}And Meimi? She may have more than a bit\Nof interest in such a determined boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:06.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122101,126856}I Hate Wedding Veils
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131944,133029}So what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:14.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133112,134238}Are you going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:17.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135073,137158}Well, I guess I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137367,139952}Thank you!\NNow that it's decided, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:32.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150338,152131}Oh! It's already full!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:35.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152382,155385}It sure is popular.\NShall we come another day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:36.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155593,156344}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:40.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156386,160515}I didn't get any last time and today,\NI wanna eat some chocolate chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:42.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161057,162934}You're acting very immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163267,164602}Yeah, just like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167438,170692}Your obsession with ice cream\Nproves your lack of maturity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171067,172527}Keep your opinion to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172819,175071}It's popular with\Ncollege girls, too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175947,178533}Those college girls\Nare just as immature as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181536,183454}Just who are "you" calling immature?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:04.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183746,184914}Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184997,186916}You're barely out of diapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186999,188835}Should we teach him\Nhow to have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189335,192338}Um… I… Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206602,208271}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208855,210106}Heaven's punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210481,211274}But still…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212442,213192}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213359,214277}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214402,215278}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215737,216779}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220116,221784}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223286,224704}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227248,228124}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228374,229459}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232587,233379}See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248853,250229}Oh, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251147,252231}I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252940,255568}What's the matter Meimi?\NYou don't look very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255985,258488}The happiness of a family\Ncomes from healthy greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258696,260782}Let's try again!\NWelcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264035,265620}I'm back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269332,270708}My new trick…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271834,272710}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279509,281219}Looks like she's in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282762,284931}Maybe she did badly on a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285807,287683}What's that jerk's problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292855,295066}Oh, Ruby, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295775,298027}I didn't mean to snap at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299862,302490}Why am I so irritated?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:06.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303449,306786}He's not supposed to\Nmean anything to me and still…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311332,312708}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:16.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313459,316420}I don't even know why I feel this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317421,318673}How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:36.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330101,336107}God, please grant my wish.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337358,338401}I'm so glad…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338609,339443}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339986,341487}Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:46.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342905,346492}Oh, how beautiful!\NIt's a wedding veil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349370,351038}It's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351664,353124}Papa, why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353291,354625}Who is it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355084,357003}Does it make you happy, Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358254,360298}The wedding veil is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360756,362383}For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362592,364510}It's a gift from your fiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366762,368264}Isn't it wonderful, Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368556,369765}Yes, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380943,383112}Meimi, Seira, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383321,384196}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384322,385114}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385239,387950}What's the matter Meimi?\NYou don't look too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388451,390202}Maybe she's found\Nthat special someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:34.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392914,394665}Who is it? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395458,397460}Today is an important day…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397668,400338}but you haven't prepared\Nfor it at all, am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401255,402381}That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402840,405176}Oh no! I haven't prepared either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405551,407720}I'm sure you're well prepared,\Naren't you, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408346,409889}Tell me, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410348,412892}Studying is something\None must do on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413267,414352}That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414894,416896}That's just how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417521,419523}You've got ten minutes\Nuntil class starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419941,421108}Excuse us…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421859,422985}Seniors…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423361,425196}They're the badminton club freshmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425780,427031}Aren't they cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427323,428699}Oh… that girl is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429450,430785}That's Sayaka Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430952,432370}She's cute and really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432912,435539}I hear she lives in an\Nold mansion at the edge of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441587,445549}Hey, I wonder what\Nshe's staring at so intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:29.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445841,449303}You're right.\NShe's staring pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:53.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469073,473369}So the wedding veil is a\Ntoken of your engagement?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:58.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474161,478624}Yes, but…\NI've never even met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:05.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481836,485006}My parents arranged\Nthe engagement themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486674,488092}You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489510,490845}On top of that I…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:13.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490970,493556}There's someone else I'm in love with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501105,502398}Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:26.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502523,506360}I don't want to be engaged\Nto a stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507194,510573}If only that veil would disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513534,514493}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:38.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514869,518497}Please give me the strength\Nto dissolve this engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519665,522209}May the blessings of God be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529258,532428}And there's nothing\NSayaka can do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:54.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533012,534180}It seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:09:00.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535097,540770}All right! St. Tail shall steal\Nthat wedding veil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:06.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541520,546275}Even if the person Sayaka\Nis in love with is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548527,551655}Gross! What terrible taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552782,554325}What are you going to do Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554867,556994}Why are you asking\Nme something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557244,558370}Then you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:22.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559121,562625}Of course not!\NSt. Tail never has second thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:26.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563167,566212}I'll steal that wedding veil,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567838,569298}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:37.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571675,577515}So you see, they completely\Ndisregarded a young girl's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578933,581852}It's unforgivable.\NIsn't that right, Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605209,607545}"Tonight, I'm going to steal a\Nwedding veil from…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607628,609380}the Shinomiya residence."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610089,611423}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612967,615553}What's all that noise\Nthis early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616554,618097}It's a vocal warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:21.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618264,621225}Forget it.\NMusic doesn't run in our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621934,623144}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:28.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625354,628732}I know I told her to\Nkeep me informed, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635072,636448}I guess I won't wash my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655384,657970}Hey, what are you doing?\NHurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659305,662266}Look, I made a really good\Nsunny-side-up egg today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:03.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662558,663517}I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:05.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664602,665811}What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:10.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666020,670065}When you make them, you grumble\Nif anything is left on the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670691,672193}I don't want to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672860,674695}A growing boy like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675029,677740}If I eat, the note might dissapear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678365,679950}I've just got some stuff going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680326,682328}What, you found yourself a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682870,684038}Don 't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:29.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684955,689668}Why do you keep your back turned?\NWhen you talk to somebody, face them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691670,694965}I've got stuff going on so… see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698385,700304}Is that really St. Tail's note?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:41.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700763,701764}That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:42.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701972,702765}Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702932,706435}But you're a real idiot, having slept\Nthrough her writing it on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706685,707728}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707895,709438}Let me touch it real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709772,711649}Stupid! Don't touch it!\NYour hands are dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711774,712775}How silly…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712858,713776}Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:58.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713943,718656}Cut it out, you idiot! Knock it off!\NShe's mine! I'm gonna get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719448,720491}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722076,723118}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:08.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724620,728457}Even if the person Sayaka\Nis in love with is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736632,737633}Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:22.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740886,742221}Asuka…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742972,743806}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:32.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748185,752189}…therefore I'd appreciate\Nyou letting me stake the place out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753274,754191}Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754441,756068}Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757152,758279}There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:44.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758654,764785}St. Tail has never gone back\Non a warning or failed in a caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765369,768038}If you take her lightly,\Nyou'll be in a terrible situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771208,773752}Let's go over the\Nplan for this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774003,776880}On top of getting the veil stolen,\NI can win over Asuka Jr., too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777047,780175}If this is the case, I wish\NMiss Thief could come every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:08.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784471,788267}Well, time to work.\NGotta help those in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801113,802239}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802865,804491}I thought I heard\Nsomething in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806785,808287}I think someone's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:32.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808912,812249}In situations like this\Nit's usually a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:35.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814168,815711}Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816837,818630}You're right. Just a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820841,822634}She's my daughter, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843614,846617}Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852164,853165}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855417,856377}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858629,859880}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:39.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876188,879274}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:41.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880776,881693}Well, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882027,884071}Are you really going Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884363,885114}I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:50.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885614,890035}If I were Sayaka, I wouldn't want\Nan engagement like that, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:56.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891954,896542}If the veil is returned, I'm sure\Nthe engagement will be called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897418,899503}Can you do it, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:03.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900295,903173}Without a doubt, if it's God's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:08.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904341,908470}This "Tail" thief is probably thinking\Nof entering through the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:16.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911515,916019}So I'm going to stand watch in the room\Ndirectly below the attic, for an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917688,920149}But, what if she enters\Nfrom a different place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921191,923193}If I say she's coming through here,\Nthat's how it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:27.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923777,927739}I've met up with her many times\Nand I know what to expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929116,931743}Are you absolutely sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934872,937458}Papa, don't be rude to Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:42.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938792,942880}Papa, Mama, will you wait outside?\NAsuka and I will keep watch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944423,945966}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946175,947759}Well, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:51.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947968,951555}I'm sure you'll be able to catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952764,954349}What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956268,958145}Okay, just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:02.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961440,962983}There's something odd…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:08.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964776,968030}St. Tail never steals without a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:12.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969281,972701}Why would she want\Nto steal a wedding veil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973118,974161}Well that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974286,975287}Mr. Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975829,977122}The inner courtyard…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984838,986590}Hurry and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:31.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987299,991178}Even if she uses a decoy\Nor some sort of camouflage…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994598,996058}there's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996391,999186}I'm not such a dimwit that I'd\Nbe caught with the same trick twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:46.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002940,1006026}He's not falling for my tricks.\NHow boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006527,1009905}Well, if he's looking for a challenge,\NI'll give him one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:02.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018664,1022751}The security is pretty bad.\NNo guards or anything so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:14.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030926,1034596}The wedding veil and\NAsuka Jr. are waiting just for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034763,1036265}One small setback.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036640,1040477}But, with the veil right in front of me,\NI can't back down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045774,1047776}St. Tail! You've taken the bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057828,1059121}Applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059913,1062916}Applause, my foot!\NThat's no fair! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064334,1066086}Let me go! She's going to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066211,1067546}But I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067671,1068797}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069131,1070924}Miss Thief, take it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071675,1073552}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077014,1078682}She's gonna escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078765,1079850}I don 't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:07.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082352,1087149}Stealing this veil means Sayaka's\Nengagement will be called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088025,1090193}It's the right thing to do, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:15.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093864,1095616}She's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102539,1104207}I'm gonna catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114051,1115177}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:41.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116428,1121933}Wait! Answer me one question!\NWhy are you stealing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:46.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123352,1126438}Are you just a thief, after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:52.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128940,1132402}Haven 't you always stolen\Nto help those in trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:56.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135572,1136948}How about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:00.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137240,1140869}How about you? Why don't you\Never understand how a girl feels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142412,1145582}If you want to know who\Nthe troubled one is, ask Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147709,1149544}You super-dingbat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153674,1155425}Ding… bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161682,1163350}She got away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:31.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167979,1171400}I won't give up!\NI'll never give in to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172526,1174528}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:45.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182369,1185789}So, St. Tail dissolved\Nthe engagement?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:51.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186873,1191211}She returned the wedding veil\Nto the sender's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:55.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191586,1195549}Then, he got angry\Nand called off the engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198093,1200137}Thank you very much, Asuka Jr.
